metadata.name: Punk Renascence #1
metadata.description: Our Punks Renascence NFT project is a tribute to all the Punks who came before us, and all other projects that played many important roles in building the NFT space to this day. This 10,000 PFP collection is the revival of Crypto Punks in a fun, unique colorful art style. We're proud to be able to share our vision for what should be cherished and appreciate everything this community has done for us.
